The aim of the seminar is to provide students with necessary skills from collecting research material and working with academic literature to writing and editing academic publications. The aim of the research seminar is to write an independent academic work in dialogue with academic supervisor and colleagues. In addition to written research, students must present presentations that are based on their research and scientific literature of the field. In the end of academic year the public defence of the seminar thesis is carried thought.Objectives/eesmärkid:  Basic overview is given on composing academic work in regular communication with academic supervisor and students of the similar topics. 
